            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Dire que, sans filtrer d'un divin Cœur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "10",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Un air divin, et qui veut que tout s'aime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "S'in-Pan-filtre, et sème",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Ces vols d'oasis folles de blasphèmes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Vivant pour toucher quelque part un Cœur…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dire que, sans filtrer d'un divin Cœur,\nUn air divin, et qui veut que tout s'aime,\nS'in-Pan-filtre, et sème\nCes vols d'oasis folles de blasphèmes\nVivant pour toucher quelque part un Cœur…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Un tic tac froid rit en nos poches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Chronomètres, réveils, coucous ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Faut remonter ces beaux joujoux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "œufs à heures, mouches du coche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Là-haut s'éparpillant en cloches…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un tic tac froid rit en nos poches,\nChronomètres, réveils, coucous ;\nFaut remonter ces beaux joujoux,\nœufs à heures, mouches du coche,\nLà-haut s'éparpillant en cloches…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Voici le soir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Grince, musique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Hypertrophique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Des remontoirs !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voici le soir,\nGrince, musique\nHypertrophique\nDes remontoirs !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Dire que Tout est un Très Sourd Mystère ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et que le Temps, qu'on ne sait où saisir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Oui, pour l'avertir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Sarcle à jamais les bons soleils martyrs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5−5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ô laps sans digues des nuits du Mystère !…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "10",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dire que Tout est un Très Sourd Mystère ;\nEt que le Temps, qu'on ne sait où saisir,\nOui, pour l'avertir !\nSarcle à jamais les bons soleils martyrs,\nÔ laps sans digues des nuits du Mystère !…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Allez, coucous, réveils, pendules ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Escadrons d'insectes d'acier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "En un concert bien familier,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Jouez sans fin des mandibules,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "L'Homme a besoin qu'on le stimule !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Allez, coucous, réveils, pendules ;\nEscadrons d'insectes d'acier,\nEn un concert bien familier,\nJouez sans fin des mandibules,\nL'Homme a besoin qu'on le stimule !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Sûrs, chaque soir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "De la musique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Hypertrophique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Des remontoirs !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sûrs, chaque soir,\nDe la musique\nHypertrophique\nDes remontoirs !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Moucherons, valseurs d'un soir de soleil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Vous, tout comme nous, nerfs de la nature,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Vous n'avez point cure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "De ce que peut être cette aventure :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5−5",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Les mondes penseurs s'errant au Soleil !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+5",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moucherons, valseurs d'un soir de soleil,\nVous, tout comme nous, nerfs de la nature,\nVous n'avez point cure\nDe ce que peut être cette aventure :\nLes mondes penseurs s'errant au Soleil !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Triturant bien l'heure en secondes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "En trois mil six cents coups de dents,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "De nos parts au gâteau du Temps",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Ne faites qu'un hachis immonde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Devant lequel on se morfonde !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Triturant bien l'heure en secondes,\nEn trois mil six cents coups de dents,\nDe nos parts au gâteau du Temps\nNe faites qu'un hachis immonde\nDevant lequel on se morfonde !"
        },
        {
